Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:10.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}媚眼橫飛的愛戀中的少女們 竟可令你心動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:15.76,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這個羞澀而矮小的男人  讓我們癡迷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:20.41,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}看著雜誌悠閒的「進退關鍵時」戀愛角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}現實哪能如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:29.97,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}透過窺視心靈的孔眼看你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:31.44,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是多麼幸運的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:34.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就像夢見被人擄走的這顆心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:36.64,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}難免也有不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:39.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}日積月累對你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:47.12,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我敢斷言  即使落入海底也能發現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.45,0:00:51.75,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}絕佳機會的現在進行時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:56.94,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}哪能放過這僅此一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:02.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}傷痕痛楚又何必在意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:06.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}事實我們無緣放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:12.49,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}絕佳機會的現在進行時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.52,0:01:17.72,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}哪能放過這僅此一次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.69,0:01:22.81,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}後悔什麼的到一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.44,0:01:27.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永恆在我們手中繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:17.05,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個賭上地球命運的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的未來都被托付在一個少年身上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日落之前能到達終點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟會迎來怎樣的結果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於牽牛花怪的襲擊  雖然一時真的捏了把汗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  結城梨斗在朋友的救援下  好像脫離了危險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來還會有怎樣的考驗在等著他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像突破重圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能大意哦  對手可是那個戴比路克王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是我一個人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來那規則就很亂七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪還有資格怪我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  既然連我都來陪你面對這種荒唐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要到達終點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古手川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  有點羨慕菈菈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救地球的英雄像白馬王子一樣來迎接自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的考驗來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地裂？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掉下去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作為戴比路克星的第一公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看到最後的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜的待在我旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是王的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就不能前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離對面還有相當大的距離啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非飛到天上去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很困擾啊  結城梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天条院學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話待會再說  快坐上來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  為什麼那麼多人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙姬大人  已經明顯超載了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意點  你在摸哪裡啊  下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下得去嗎  而且又不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過多虧你幫忙呢  天条院同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是看到我們的狀況所以來救援的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的對手永遠都是菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城梨斗如果贏了這個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等同於我贏了菈菈父女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正說得高興呢  能不能不要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼不講理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們搞清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是擔心結城梨斗  或者說菈菈不在會覺得寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙姬大人  前方有不明飛行物接近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掉下去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色闇影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  金色闇影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的目標  我只是不想讓你被別的人殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  好像沒有能在這裡停留的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情變糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城梨斗他們平安無事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜  在的話回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里紗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼  我們也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  即使我去了也幫不上什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  我們也…  不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有春菜才能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡呆呆地看著電視轉播也沒有意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先去了再說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等  里紗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是接下來怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就料到會有這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出租車？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  快點  上車上車
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里紗  屁股又大了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  你也快點上來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司機  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾位客人  要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司機  去結城君那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  抓好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO  GO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先藏在那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我經歷這樣的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈父女倆  給我記著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  到了這裡總能小鬆一口氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也說不准呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話由你來說一點都不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我覺得現在更加危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡讓我們來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:07:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能幹一場了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你盡快去公主那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊無效？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快點去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去菈菈那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去  結城梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能闖過葫蘆怪這一關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:09:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既有判斷力又有膽識
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼著命來幫助他的人有那麼多  確實在我意料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  快停下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要傷害我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有手下留情不至於奪走他們性命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些史萊姆  也不過是讓他們在日落之前無法動彈而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼  衣服都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也沒有做到這種地步的理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊  有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩這個遊戲的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要起到表率作用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到目的地了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先做個夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.35,0:10:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城梨斗不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為那個奇怪的植物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還能再次動起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離決定我們人類命運的日落不到一個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場遊戲究竟會演變成怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終會有怎樣的結果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈…菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:10:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是怎麼回事  話說為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是裸的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.35,0:11:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家都是裸體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好嗎  這樣怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君  放輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這…這種
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  是夢  一定是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心在砰砰跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為梨斗看上去很困擾  我們兩個就決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸…胸部都碰到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君是在認真地考慮我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點我們知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是負起男人的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣的結果一定會有一個人傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做梨斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做結城君的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來誰都不會受傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會好好相處的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  但是  這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能想得太複雜哦  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說  不喜歡我們三個人一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:12:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  睜開眼睛吧  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  小春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於知道自己的想法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣  如果梨斗想那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們不管什麼樣的結果都能接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  結城君  還差一點就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  小春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩斯丁  幾點了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6點14分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉勉強強趕上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去迎接勝利者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  梨斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好  結城梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:17:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論生老病死  你都能尊敬她  愛她  真心對她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  突然變這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你實現了和我的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成遊戲  證明了你是宇宙第一的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…宇宙第一？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承認你是宇宙第一愛菈菈的男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼不滿的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確是喜歡菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不僅僅是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼問題  啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說的是…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是梨斗的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會和梨斗結婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無視梨斗的感情  單方面的婚姻是不會幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼話  這小子可是你的未婚夫呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經覺得這樣下去就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  果然還是不能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是這個婚約讓梨斗受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈大人  您不能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為戴比路克第一公主  在此宣佈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈·薩塔琳·戴比路克  和結城梨斗解除婚約
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這意味著什麼意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  地球要根據婚約解除條例  被爆破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  我不會讓這樣的事發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  要用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜記憶君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個把地球上的各位所有關於我的記憶消除
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  菈菈  這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  未婚妻什麼的  我想撇開這些因素
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從頭開始努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜  還有大家能和我做朋友  謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  我從一開始就知道了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗是宇宙第一溫柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很喜歡你哦  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大家早安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要介紹一位新轉來的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的好嗎  菈菈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  但是只能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  初次見面  我是今天轉到這個學校的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？大家都沒有忘記嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了  你的發明有成功過嗎  哼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  今後  也多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜  那個時候沒說完的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後  也多多關照哦  結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:20.01,EDJA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}水玉は愛され模様
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:23.49,EDJA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこだって生きてゆけるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:30.44,EDJA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大切な私のお守りよ連れて行って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:34.43,EDJA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}旅をして君のもとまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.57,0:22:37.99,EDJA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}波に乗ってぐんぐんどこまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:45.58,EDJA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}水玉は言ったわ　愛するとは時に醜くもあると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.82,0:22:52.80,EDJA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}踏み出す足　小さく震える地面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:23:02.54,EDJA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}答えなど要らない　この想い消えないかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.51,0:23:07.54,EDJA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}星にララバイ　歌ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:11.20,EDJA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君とバイバイ　できるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:18.28,EDJA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘯いた空　嘘つきはどこ？　水玉と目が合った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.49,0:23:22.05,EDJA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今ララバイ　歌ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:27.23,EDJA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君とバイバイ　できるはずはないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:36.79,EDJA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い乗せ　君に届くよ　ラッキーチューン
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:20.01,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}水珠滾滾的可愛波紋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:23.49,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}活蹦亂跳地無限延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:30.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}還有帶著我重要的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:34.43,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}展開以你為終點的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.57,0:22:37.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}乘著波浪不斷前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:45.58,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}水珠說過 有時愛情也會顯得不美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.82,0:22:52.80,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}邁步前行  地面也微震輕鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.94,0:23:02.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無需任何回答  這份思念不會消淡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.51,0:23:07.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}輕吟搖籃曲  陪伴星星入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:11.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我可下定決心  向你說聲再見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:18.33,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大叫後的天空下  誰在撒謊？  我和水珠相互對視
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.49,0:23:22.05,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}輕吟搖籃曲  一人墮入夢鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:27.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我怎麼可能下定決心  向你說再見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:36.79,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}添上這思念  願能傳到你身邊  LUCKY CHU～
